" Let the IDE handle ctrl+n/p/y for popup navigation (code actions, completions)
sethandler <C-n> n:vim i:ide v:ide
sethandler <C-p> n:vim i:ide v:ide
sethandler <C-y> n:vim i:ide v:ide

" Paste in visual mode without yanking replaced text
xmap p "_dP
